data.description: Exclusive Wateroak condominium w/seasonal lake view just five minutes to Prairie Creek Marina & minutes to Downtown Rogers. Primary bedroom / bath on main level plus guest room & bath. Formal dining or second living area on main level. Gas fireplace in living room. Downstairs features a bedroom & bath and a huge game room & was recently remodeled w/new paint, new laminate flooring & walk in shower. Large amounts of storage (walk in closets, built ins, pantry) can be found throughout the home. Spacious decks for outdoor entertaining. Workshop area located in basement. Hot tub to be removed. Short term rentals not allowed. For sale only, home is not for rent.
